steps.name: I want to create a new Member
I fill the information of the Member "Laura Ortega","lulu345@gmail.com","Es profesora en la universidad de los andes"
I should see the Member published
I want to create a new Post
I fill the information Post "Caballo de pelo largo 2","Los hermosos caballos con gran melena que se pasean por Cartagena y corren como un ferrari"
I should see the post published
I want to edit a Post

I fill the information Post "Costa Rica el paraiso","Ubicado en el corazon de centro america con una geografa accidentada, que incluye bosques tropicales y costas en el Caribe y el Pacfico. Aunque su capital, San Jos, es hogar de instituciones culturales, como el Museo del Oro Precolombino"
I should see the Post Updated
I want to delete a Member
I select the delete Member option
I should see the Member deleted
